    {
      "name": "Frenzied Rockslide",
      "description": "The final hit of a Normal Attack combo triggers a collapse, dealing 60% of ATK as AoE Geo DMG.",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/UI_Talent_S_PlayerRock_06.png"
    },
    {
      "name": "Foreign Adamantine",
      "description": "Draw new strength from journeys past. For every element you have resonated with, you gain additional buffs.\n\nAdditionally, when nearby party members become protected by a shield, when the shield is replaced for any reason, or when Geo Constructs are created, the Traveler will receive 1 stack of Blade of Archaic Petra, max 3 stacks. Up to 1 stack may be obtained every second in this way. After obtaining 3 stacks of Blade of Archaic Petra, performing a Charged Attack will consume all stacks of Blade of Archaic Petra and transform into the special Charged Attack: Rockfell.\n\nCharged Attack: Rockfell\n· Each Charged Attack hit deals increased Geo DMG. Increase in DMG is equal to 120% of Traveler's ATK.\n· For 15s after hitting an opponent, nearby party members will have their shield strength temporarily increased by 20%.\n· Charged Attack: Rockfell can be triggered up to once every 15s.",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/UI_Talent_S_PlayerRock_07.png"
    }
  ],
  "constellations": [
    {
      "name": "Invincible Stonewall",
      "description": "Party members within the radius of Wake of Earth have their CRIT Rate increased by 10% and have increased resistance against interruption.",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/UI_Talent_S_PlayerRock_01.png"
    },
